  5. Waiver Wire vs. Free Agents is unexplained. Same Roster page. Two tabs side by side: "Free Agents (447)" and "Waiver Wire." I have no idea what the difference is. No tooltip, no subtitle, no inline explanation.

  **How to fix (UX-020):** In `app/team/[teamId]/roster/RosterManager.tsx`, add a short subtitle or inline tooltip to each tab:
  - "Free Agents" → subtitle: "Players not on any team — immediate add during the season."
  - "Waiver Wire" → subtitle: "Recently dropped players — claimed by priority order over 48 hours."
  These can be added as `<span>` subtext lines under each tab label, or as a small info banner at the top of each tab's content area. No backend changes needed.

  **Covered by:** UX-020 (net-new)

